                    <p> Republican front-runner Donald Trump once again lashed out at Muslims on Wednesday. </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> &quot;I think Islam hates us,&quot; the billionaire told CNN's Anderson Cooper when asked whether the religion was &quot;at war with the West.&quot; </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> &quot;We have to get to the bottom of it,&quot; Trump said. &quot;There is an unbelievable hatred of us — anybody.&quot; </p>
                
              
                    <div class="ad-container ad-container_default ad-container_mobile ad-hide">
                      <div class="ad-label ad-hide">
                      	<a href="http://www.nbcnews.com/id/31066137/media-kit/" target="_blank">advertisement</a>
